<title>lw mhmạ kạnt</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr - lw mhmạ kạnt ṣʿbẗ ẓrwfy rạḥ gẖnylk
 lw mhmạ kạnt ạ̉yạmy swdạ bṣlylk
 rgẖm ạlạ̉lm wạlḍyq rạḥ ạ̹rfʿ ạsmk bạlʿạly
 wtwb ạlḥzn ạlʿtyq qlʿth ʿsẖạnk yạ gẖạly
 ạ̉bdạaⁿ msẖ rạḥ yḥnyny ḍʿfy wḥzny wạ̉nyny
 wlạ rạḥ tsẖmt fy ẓrwfy lw mhmạ kạnt
 1- ạ̉nạ fkẖry ạ̹nh bḍʿfy qwh ạ̹lhy btẓhr
 wạljbl ạlʿạly ạlly qdạmy ʿly̱ ạsmh ydwb wyṣgẖr
 myn ạ̹nt yạ bḥr ạlhạyj yswʿ byjy mạsẖy fwqk
 myn ạ̹nt yạ swry ạlʿạly bạ̹lhy bạṭlʿ fwqk
 2- ạ̉nạ bdy ạlʿạlm yʿrf ạ̹nh ạlly mṭmn qlby
 lw bạ̉twn ạlnạr wwạqf yạ ạ̹lhy bsẖwfk jnby
 lạ ạlmwt wlạ ạlmrḍ byqdr yḥnyny wyksr ly rạsy
 ʿslạmy yswʿ byshr whw ḍạmnly kẖlạṣy</lyrics>
